creator: The Tifin Group LLC
descriptionHtml:
Magnifi delivers access to in-depth data, insights and investing intelligence, so you can quickly find what you’re looking for and buy with confidence.

DISCOVER, COMPARE & BUY INVESTMENTS
- Explore 15,000+ stocks, ETFs and mutual funds to focus on the investments that match your goals.
- Find investments that fit your interests
- Compare based on risk, returns and fees
- Optimize intelligence from industry-leading data sources
- Instantly invest or add to your watchlist

NEXT-LEVEL INVESTING INTELLIGENCE
For only $14/month, add Magnifi Personal to your account to empower your investing with 24/7 personalized insights, guidance and planning tools.

- Ask questions about investing terms, trends and strategies
- Stay on top of the market with personalized alerts
- Build your own portfolio, guided by AI
- Optimize your portfolio with actionable insights and investment opportunities

COMMISSION-FREE INVESTING
When you’re ready to put your research and intelligence to work, you can seamlessly buy and sell investments with your Magnifi Investing Account. US citizens over the age of 18 can invest in stocks, ETFs, mutual funds and more including fractional shares and low minimum investments. Magnifi does not charge commissions or fees.

Disclosures: Magnifi LLC does not charge advisory fees or transaction fees for non-managed accounts. Please see Magnifi’s Form ADV for additional information about fees and charges that may apply. Mutual funds or ETFs may have additional fees or expenses. You should review the fund’s prospectus before investing. While Magnifi does not charge commissions or fees on stocks, ETFs or mutual funds, the custodian of your account may charge separately for certain services. Any custodial fees or charges are contained in your customer account agreement.
